autocmd Filetype markdown,rmd inoremap ,l --------<Enter>
autocmd Filetype rmd inoremap ,r ```{r}<CR>```<CR><CR><esc>2kO
autocmd Filetype rmd inoremap ,p ```{python}<CR>```<CR><CR><esc>2kO
